\f1\b bh\uc0\u363  \'84a fi, a deveni\'94
\f0\b0 \
Acest verb poate \'eensemna fie \'84a exista\'94, fie \'84a lua na\uc0\u537 tere\'94:\
\uc0\u2325 \u2381 \u2352 \u2379 \u2343 \u2366 \u2340 \u2381  \u2349 \u2357 \u2340 \u2367  \u2360 \u2350 \u2381 \u2350 \u2379 \u2361 \u2307 \u8232 krodh\u257 t bhavati sammohah\u803 \u8232 \'84Din furie se na\u537 te iluzia.\'94\

